{"tid":159337,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"電影版《聲之形》上映在即 《你的名字》新海誠讚嘆：根本模仿不來","createTime":"2017-03-17T01:54:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T09:59:26.000Z","uid":9573,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42a9a55b2aba9dc5c971dae67b8b0d2ac6b11ed6","tid":159337,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:54:55.000Z","msg":"動漫迷照過來！照過來！繼電影《你的名字》交換靈魂的感人故事後，又有一支催淚強片誕生啦～那就是改編自日本女漫畫家大今良時暢銷漫畫《聲之形》的同名動畫電影作品《電影版聲之形》！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63673/58c8aa1ca3375.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63673%2F58c8aa1ca3375.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=e6cab2fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該片在日本當地上映後，票房就開出高達 23 億日圓（約新台幣 6 億 2500 萬元）的紅盤，成功擊退導演新海誠的《你的名字》，並奪下今年「東京動畫獎」最佳動畫電影、最佳編劇兩項大獎，掀起了動漫界一陣轟動，如今這部人人傳頌的神作終於要在3月24號來台感動獻映囉。事不宜遲，快跟著小編一起來看看《電影版聲之形》到底有什麼驚人之處吧！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63673/58c8aa4b13182.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63673%2F58c8aa4b13182.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=7408d529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《電影版聲之形》內容是在描述一名憤世嫉俗的少年「石田將也」，因為極度厭惡「無聊」，所以時常把「開朗！愉快！大冒險！」當成座右銘，並帶頭欺負一位班上聽障轉學生「西宮硝子」，直到將也一次無心的惡作劇，反而讓自己成為被全班孤立的對象，從此將也便關起心房，漸漸成了孤獨少年。五年後，將升上高中，下定決心結束自己了無生趣的人生，但是在在死前，將也希望見硝子一面，並當面向她道歉，然而這個心願，卻在與硝子重逢後意外起了微妙變化&hellip;。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63673/58c8aa2051ac8.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63673%2F58c8aa2051ac8.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=97b95841&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如何？看到這是否已經讓你「漫」心蕩漾了啊～不過不說你可能不知道，《電影版聲之形》的原著漫畫雖然早在 2008 年就入選第 80 屆「週刊少年Magazine新人漫畫獎」，還曾連續 2 年榮登「這本漫畫真厲害！」男性部門冠軍寶座。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63673/58c8aa1d63188.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63673%2F58c8aa1d63188.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=30604d42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但故事因為涉及「霸凌」與歧視「聽障」等敏感議題，所以在日本引發極大關注，導致漫畫一度石沈大海，無法刊登出版，還好在《別冊少年Magazine》主編積極爭取下，《聲之形》終於在 2011 年問世。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63673/58c8aa21ca173.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63673%2F58c8aa21ca173.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=f01e4cd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對此，大今良時強調，自己想表達的中心思想其實是「人與人之間，相互傳達心意的困難。」所以為了表現這種意境，才讓女主角成為「難以表達自己心意」的聽障角色，並且遭到男主角欺負。<br />\n<img src=\"http://zhongwen.astro.com.my/Portals/21/Images/ArticleImages/2012102911346691/2047%20625X385.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzhongwen.astro.com.my%2FPortals%2F21%2FImages%2FArticleImages%2F2012102911346691%2F2047%2520625X385.JPG&h=3022a972&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而大今良時也希望，觀眾在理解故事背後的底蘊後，能在最貼近現實的社會議題中明白人心交流的可貴，並且學習到彼此尊重與包容，保持真摯、良善自我的重要性，讓悲苦生命從此慢慢綻放溫暖。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63673/58c8aa1faa918.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63673%2F58c8aa1faa918.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=c71cc617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如此富含教育意義又發人深省的原著，讓同名電影《電影版聲之形》在國外上映後引發一連串討論，而且好評不斷，連《你的名字》導演新海誠都慕名上電影院欣賞，看完後甚至在自己推特大讚，「這是一部非常棒的作品，到處都充滿認真細緻的構思，畫風、色彩和情感也呈現得十分唯美。高雅端正的演出，是別人想模仿也模仿不來的。還有配音演員也很棒，我個人對入野自由的演技大吃一驚。我非常喜歡。」 此話一出，當然隨即又引爆網友對《電影版聲之形》的暴動。<br />\n<br />\n▼《電影版聲之形》的預告、完整版主題曲「恋をしたのは」～請享用！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_I-3nh9cU2U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_I-3nh9cU2U&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9HadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=e00d2d90\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_I-3nh9cU2U</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/koenokatachi.movie/videos/1296716013701858/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkoenokatachi.movie%2Fvideos%2F1296716013701858%2F&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9HadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=3d182f20\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/koenokatachi.movie/videos/1296716013701858/</a>"},{"pid":"bbc6dad1afe8af7f391425d3cfde10c1722d953e","tid":159337,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6949e951bbb77099cf911c82e29576daaec71c6c","tid":159337,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T02:05:43.000Z","msg":"唔想啲MK垃圾偽毒仆去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64656aafcce75e7fbe4afe710d11b296be3a5c6","tid":159337,"uid":20963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T02:09:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔想啲MK垃圾偽毒仆去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a9ee94ed3832bf5e5db1b84f4a70b9c4f45efd","tid":159337,"uid":31307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T02:09:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔想啲MK垃圾偽毒仆去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n希望啲MK唔識欣賞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d8a2f1292136da71954cedec38a867fb583d8af","tid":159337,"uid":1177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T02:12:49.000Z","msg":"買左四號場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 期待"},{"pid":"d45817a8d6e1d6eb3a07a90cfabb84db07e8c8c1","tid":159337,"uid":37713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T02:17:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔想啲MK垃圾偽毒仆去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" cla